title: Cheesy Double Hasselback Chicken with Courgette & Capsicum Traybake
description: Get ready for a bite of cheesy perfection! Juicy, golden chicken in a show-stopping smokey spice blend, topped with ooey gooey melted cheese. Nestled alongside tender courgette and sweet capsicum, this one-pan wonder is packed with bold flavours and minimal fuss.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
